item.title: Hydrodynamic model output and image simulation code for evaluating image-based river velocimetry from a case study on the Sacramento River near Glenn, California
item.description: Abstract This data release includes the data and code used for the manuscript titled “A framework to facilitate development and testing of image-based river velocimetry algorithms”, submitted to the journal Earth Surface Processes and Landforms. Three *.csv files and five *.m files with MATLAB source code are included below.
